[{"pos": "epubcfi(/12/2/4[3Q280-ac1f865aed64466fba6f619b636b614b]/2/1:1)", "pos_type": "epubcfi", "timestamp": "2022-02-26T07:29:39.306484+00:00", "type": "last-read"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-09T14:04:37.003Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "-Ft1hn7tZYISuhSX3vALfg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/212/1:106", "highlighted_text": "所有这三个波段都具有25000～30000GHz的带宽", "notes": "相当于每秒能发送 25000*1000*1000*1000个bit ,也就是每秒能发送 3T左右的数据!!!\n\n等等!\n\n此处的带宽并不直接等于发送速率!!", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/212/1:79", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T08:03:40.955Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.1 导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "3TUYGq-0CfMIZwO-2Xopdw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/324/1:344", "highlighted_text": "现在已经有了很好的掺铒光纤放大器EDFA（Erbium Doped Fiber Amplifier）。它是一种光放大器，不需要像以前那样复杂，先把光信号转换成电信号，经过电放大器放大后，再转换成为光信号。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/324/1:249", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T08:04:53.385Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.4 信道复用技术", "2.4.2 波分复用"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "5JkZE99A9RYF3HCr9nTuhg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/674/1:57", "highlighted_text": "网络层把运输层产生的报文段或用户数据报封装成分组或包进行传送。", "notes": "把报文拆分成分组数据包, 应该是由操作系统提供的底层功能直接完成的, 应用层代码无需考虑? 那如何调优拆分的数据包大小等等因数呢?", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/674/1:29", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:09:16.193Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "5wmfTMfmYOzkbpD-w91agA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/678/1:53", "highlighted_text": "网络层的另一个任务就是要选择合适的路由，使源主机运输层所传下来的分组，能够通过网络中的路由器找到目的主机。", "notes": "所以网络层应该不考虑TCP,UDP等数据包, 只考虑IP数据包吧?\n网络链路上的各路由器,只是拿IP数据包来处理?", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/678/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:12:40.116Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "6bztsX29aUARORxT4SqH3Q"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:26:29.619Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "78gaBwCZz6wEgYS61-8FsQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/88/1:51", "highlighted_text": "来自信源的信号常称为基带信号（即基本频带信号）。像计算机输出的代表各种文字或图像文件的数据信号都属于基带信号。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/88/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:10:30.063Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.2 数据通信的基础知识", "2.2.2 有关信道的几个基本概念"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "79YtIfTOpjqhY6w4lfsLDw"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2022-02-26T07:21:34.752Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "7FOdKrEOkpCTtFvyxo2MzQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/274/1:40", "highlighted_text": "在十分偏远的地方，或在离大陆很远的海洋中，要进行通信就几乎完全要依赖于卫星通信。", "notes": "想象一下, 在远离大陆的海洋通过卫星通讯上网, 延迟至少200,300ms, 那也是醉了", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/274/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:55:02.976Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.2 非导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "7dn1lTTs9PSqkD6uF5A4Xg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/82/2:87", "highlighted_text": "接收端在收到物理层上交的比特流后，就能根据首部和尾部的标记，从收到的比特流中识别帧的开始和结束。", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/82/2:39", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:45:46.615Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.2 三个基本问题"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "9H-Au3qsNsf7yTA-oQdiDA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/668/4/2:80", "highlighted_text": "用户数据报协议UDP（User Datagram Protocol）——提供无连接的、尽最大努力（best-effort）的数据传输服务（不保证数据传输的可靠性），其数据传输的单位是用户数据报。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/668/4/2/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:04:14.320Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "9tdIEMWltM1MgippVKh2Jw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/582/1:316", "highlighted_text": "现今规模最大的、覆盖全球的、基于TCP/IP的互联网并未使用OSI标准", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/582/1:281", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:48:18.267Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.1 计算机网络体系结构的形成"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "B_x1QBUUFuzIbSe0wcHRkw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/702/1:232", "highlighted_text": "传送比特流时应从首部开始传送。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/702/1:217", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:23:39.360Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "BwOKoMsSFmLc6iYzaOagcA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/196/1:108", "highlighted_text": "由于可见光的频率非常高，约为108MHz的量级，因此一个光纤通信系统的传输带宽远远大于目前其他各种传输媒体的带宽。", "notes": "频率高意味着,单位时间内能发送的数据更多, 表现为发送数据快, 但传播数据的速度甚至不如铜线!!!", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/196/1:52", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:30:36.860Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.1 导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "CRBk6etyfEBsiTEOiTckww"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/592/1:214", "highlighted_text": "一个新标准的出现，有时不一定反映其技术水平是最先进的，而是往往有着一定的市场背景。", "notes": "5G技术呢!!!", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/592/1:173", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:47:29.464Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.1 计算机网络体系结构的形成"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "ChPy0ZRBIEXnK5ZBsF2F2w"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/480/1:94", "highlighted_text": "然而对于高速网络链路，我们提高的仅仅是数据的发送速率而不是比特在链路上的传播速率。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/480/1:91", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:04:53.785Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.6 计算机网络的性能", "1.6.1 计算机网络的性能指标"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "DYGLSBz8KOSdMrudhd586w"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/68/1:29", "highlighted_text": "首部", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/68/1:27", "style": {"kind": "decoration", "type": "builtin", "which": "wavy"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:40:39.828Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.1 数据链路和帧"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "DxElJnH1i6B3_OUGuepBuQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/762/1:122", "highlighted_text": "实际上现在的互联网使用的TCP/IP体系结构有时已经演变成为图1-23所示的那样，即某些应用程序可以直接使用IP层，或甚至直接使用最下面的网络接口层［PETE11］，图1-23是这种表示方法。", "notes": "比如某应用直接修改了IP数据包, 把IP数据包的目标地址更改了?!!!", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/762/1:26", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:33:32.856Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.5 TCP/IP的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "EGtwZrDa_q9Ih4B5it6qYw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/674/8/1:5", "highlighted_text": "分组也叫做IP数据报", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/674/1:82", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:06:21.841Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "F5JhAaTZ4wiBQQHpwwfv1Q"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/68/1:32", "highlighted_text": "尾部", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/68/1:30", "style": {"kind": "decoration", "type": "builtin", "which": "wavy"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:40:42.797Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.1 数据链路和帧"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "H_PYRi0aJDB-BamZHdouyg"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:35:20.713Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "HiaEUbkK5Lm93A2H9gFYog"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:54:59.774Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "JWthqcrQnGIi-Qwz_pHaig"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/694/1:229", "highlighted_text": "请注意，传递信息所利用的一些物理媒体，如双绞线、同轴电缆、光缆、无线信道等，并不在物理层协议之内而是在物理层协议的下面。因此也有人把物理层下面的物理媒体当作第0层。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/694/1:147", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:17:04.444Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "Jn9Ym4apraKKH98vNM15VQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/728/1:44", "highlighted_text": "服务是“垂直的”，即服务是由下层向上层通过层间接口提供的。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/728/4/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:27:42.940Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.4 实体、协议、服务和服务访问点"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "JxvillfbY-lAmGFuO_ZopA"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-09T14:04:31.652Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "L0g8Wa8YKPueA_TUGUpTVg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/580/1:180", "highlighted_text": "他们提出了一个试图使各种计算机在世界范围内互连成网的标准框架，即著名的开放系统互连基本参考模型OSI/RM（Open Systems Interconnection Reference Model），简称为OSI。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/580/1:85", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:43:42.449Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.1 计算机网络体系结构的形成"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "LpVHakkQxU_pTZe7G7uFrQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/60/1:76", "highlighted_text": "网络层协议数据单元就是IP数据报（或简称为数据报、分组或包）。", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/60/1:52", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:38:49.113Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.1 数据链路和帧"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "MbRyaNq9kbJqCBeBmG8mHg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/20/1:53", "highlighted_text": "物理层考虑的是怎样才能在连接各种计算机的传输媒体上传输数据比特流，而不是指具体的传输媒体。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/20/1:8", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:40:02.406Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.1 物理层的基本概念"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "OnkNDl_B7g9o6JHINtunVA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/648/2:151", "highlighted_text": "体系结构的英文名词architecture的原意是建筑学或建筑的设计和风格。它和一个具体的建筑物的概念很不相同。", "notes": "思考\n计算机体系结构\n计算机组成\n计算机实现\n三者的关系", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/648/2:95", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:55:54.164Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.2 协议与划分层次"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "PAXl-kfnFAq5bYM5p3rCRQ"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:04:05.040Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "Qt05G3iAtzsZM6iC2YDM2g"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:36:05.048Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "R5T5UAfmZba9PRT-SbII5w"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/208/1:97", "highlighted_text": "实际上，只要从纤芯中射到纤芯表面的光线的入射角大于某个临界角度，就可产生全反射。因此，可以存在多条不同角度入射的光线在一条光纤中传输。这种光纤就称为多模光纤（图2-10（a））", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/208/1:13", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:35:28.433Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.1 导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "RefwGSGMr7QOpNK5NHuYBQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/270/1:108", "highlighted_text": "卫星通信的另一特点就是具有较大的传播时延。由于各地球站的天线仰角并不相同，因此不管两个地球站之间的地面距离是多少（相隔一条街或相隔上万公里），从一个地球站经卫星到另一地球站的传播时延在250～300ms之间。一般可取为270ms。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/270/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:52:45.075Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.2 非导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "S3rjrVH6OXztpF4zACKEPg"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:06:26.461Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "SIgRLMRQSdgOBtPOno1b8A"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/652/3:75", "highlighted_text": "OSI的七层协议体系结构（图1-18（a））的概念清楚，理论也较完整，但它既复杂又不实用。TCP/IP体系结构则不同，但它现在却得到了非常广泛的应用。", "notes": "一直以为现在用的是OSI的七层模型!!!", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/652/3:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:58:23.591Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "TDHOhOBc07r0SY2z-SKkLg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/52/2:11", "highlighted_text": "数据链路（data link）", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/52/2/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "green"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:36:12.727Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.1 数据链路和帧"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "U7NMtdyu6sGQ0f3F4xVdjQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/670/1:131", "highlighted_text": "顺便指出，有人愿意把运输层称为传输层，理由是这一层使用的TCP协议就叫做传输控制协议。从意思上看，传输和运输差别也不大。但OSI定义的第4层使用的是Transport，而不是Transmission。这两个字的含义还是有些差别。因此，使用运输层这个译名较为准确。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/670/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:06:29.813Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "VGbhSPdN-LJNP_6hI1PWGw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/50/1:8", "highlighted_text": "所谓链路（link）", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/50/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "green"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:36:09.887Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层", "3.1 使用点对点信道的数据链路层", "3.1.1 数据链路和帧"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "ZxUvFoHraNGihs3OQf7Q3A"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/190/1:79", "highlighted_text": "在局域网发展的初期曾广泛地使用同轴电缆作为传输媒体。但随着技术的进步，在局域网领域基本上都采用双绞线作为传输媒体。目前同轴电缆主要用在有线电视网的居民小区中。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/190/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T07:27:14.283Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.3 物理层下面的传输媒体", "2.3.1 导引型传输媒体"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "f-8TuLQkcgP45sx95DrAQA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/668/2/2:73", "highlighted_text": "传输控制协议TCP（Transmission Control Protocol）——提供面向连接的、可靠的数据传输服务，其数据传输的单位是报文段（segment）。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/668/2/2/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:04:08.449Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "f2nBXJaX24UGn2z573lv_A"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/700/4/1:18", "highlighted_text": "图1-19　数据在各层之间的传递过程", "notes": "由此可见, 路由器确实是工作在IP层, 而不关心TCP,UDP等运输层东西, 更不关心当前的IP数据包是哪种应用的数据", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/700/4/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "purple"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:22:31.596Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "h6zYaweeKJqP79YOSkLH5g"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:04:10.545Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "hRohHk5a3skzzyXLMHDmiQ"}, {"removed": true, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:43:37.671Z", "type": "highlight", "uuid": "i8F5ENn-1ifDCewrN78uPg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/412/1:121", "highlighted_text": "网络技术中的速率指的是数据的传送速率，它也称为数据率（data rate）或比特率（bit rate）。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/412/1:84", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T08:09:49.672Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.6 计算机网络的性能", "1.6.1 计算机网络的性能指标"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "j-65gwXYvx2tNdrm_rZOJQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/604/1:17", "highlighted_text": "（1）语法，即数据与控制信息的结构或格式；\n\n（2）语义，即需要发出何种控制信息，完成何种动作以及做出何种响应；\n\n（3）同步，即事件实现顺序的详细说明。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/600/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T05:49:30.708Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.2 协议与划分层次"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "janLmVlXAm8uF4GvqwZl0g"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/728/1:22", "highlighted_text": "协议是“水平的”，即协议是控制对等实体之间通信的规则。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/728/2/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:27:36.580Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.4 实体、协议、服务和服务访问点"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "rebkkqIW_KOsV33wZFbFmg"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/426/1:109", "highlighted_text": "目前在欧洲，这种超高速DSL的接入方式很受欢迎。这是因为在欧洲，具有历史意义的古老建筑非常之多，而各国政府都已制定了很严格的保护文物的法律。如果为了实现高速上网就在这些古老建筑的墙上钻洞铺设光缆，那么就破坏了文物，因而被法律禁止。值得注意的是，这些国家的电话普及率很高，进入这些建筑的电话线都早已铺设好了。因此，利用现有电话线来实现高速接入，在欧洲就特别受到欢迎。\n\n在我国，情况有些不同。在建设新的高楼时，就已经把各种电缆的管线位置预留好了。因此，高楼中的用户可以根据自己的需要选择合适的接入方式（不一定非要采用xDSL技术）。因此上述这种超高速的DSL接入方式在国内使用得尚不普遍。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/424/1:0", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T08:28:12.151Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.6 宽带接入技术", "2.6.1 ADSL技术"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "uM2DklSmN4fFqEDsfY5QJw"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-372d2f2f4e0e4bfb90bee137e7bea24d]/652/1:302", "highlighted_text": "因此在学习计算机网络的原理时往往采取折中的办法，即综合OSI和TCP/IP的优点，采用一种只有五层协议的体系结构（图1-18（c）），这样既简洁又能将概念阐述清楚(12)。有时为了方便，也可把最底下两层称为网络接口层。", "spine_index": 6, "spine_name": "text/part0005.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[4OIQ0^-372d2f2f4e0e4bfb90bee137e7bea24d]/652/1:197", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-09T14:04:41.792Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第1章 概述", "1.7 计算机网络体系结构", "1.7.3 具有五层协议的体系结构"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "wRnxfREN9gHTx7fG6dUbqQ"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/50/4/2:94", "highlighted_text": "现在很多计算机使用内置的调制解调器（包含调制器和解调器），用户在计算机外面看不见调制解调器。", "spine_index": 7, "spine_name": "text/part0006.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[5N3C0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/50/4/2:48", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "red"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T06:45:50.114Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第2章 物理层", "2.2 数据通信的基础知识", "2.2.1 数据通信系统的模型"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "xk5YbjC1WfmXTujADVtJOA"}, {"end_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/12/1:153", "highlighted_text": "在本章中我们研究的是在同一个局域网中，分组怎样从一台主机传送到另一台主机，但并不经过路由器转发。从整个互联网来看，局域网仍属于数据链路层的范围。", "spine_index": 8, "spine_name": "text/part0007.html", "start_cfi": "/2/4[6LJU0^-e4c78c89259646069d91c65a5aa90a05]/12/1:81", "style": {"kind": "color", "type": "builtin", "which": "blue"}, "timestamp": "2021-02-08T09:27:39.593Z", "toc_family_titles": ["第3章 数据链路层"], "type": "highlight", "uuid": "zpLPyqso7iLiMPMudl6u-A"}]